and I couldn't resist.

1068
01:09:06,425 --> 01:09:08,784
No, no. I just can't believe
that I left it out like this.

1069
01:09:08,864 --> 01:09:10,224
Tripp, where are you?

1070
01:09:10,264 --> 01:09:13,144
