that America's children...

1455
01:33:48,704 --> 01:33:50,263
have you for a teacher.

1456
01:33:50,343 --> 01:33:52,903
Nobody teaches
a writer anything.

1457
01:33:53,023 --> 01:33:54,863
You tell 'em what you know.

1458
01:33:54,943 --> 01:33:56,823
You tell 'em to find their voice
and stay with it.

1459
01:33:56,903 --> 01:33:58,782
You tell the ones
that have it to keep at it.

1460
01:33:58,862 --> 01:34:00,742
You tell the ones that don't
have it to keep at it too...

1461
01:34:00,822 --> 01:34:04,382
because that's the only way they're
gonna get to where they're going.

1462
01:34:04,502 --> 01:34:08,381
Of course, it does help
if you know where you wanna go.

1463
01:34:09,741 --> 01:34:13,500
Helping my students
figure that out...

1464
01:34:13,580 --> 01:34:16,500
that and Sara...

1465
01:34:16,580 --> 01:34:20,259
that's what's made
these last years worthwhile.

1466
01:34:23,259 --> 01:34:26,778
As for James, well,
he doesn't really need me anymore.

1467
01:34:26,858 --> 01:34:28,698
He's got you.

1468
01:34:30,218 --> 01:34:34,777
